title: 12 OCLOCK HIGH - 113 - The Suspected
description:
OK guys...In an effort to get this series moving again I\&#039;m uploading one of the missing episodes, 113, as it seems noone else is willing or able to do so.  I apologize in advance for the file size.  I don\&#039;t feel this video quality is quite on a par with the others that have been uploaded although it is good.  But any attempt to lower the file size degraded the quality too much for my liking.

Here\&#039;s the catch...if you guys don\&#039;t start seeding Season 1 and 2 again I won\&#039;t be uploading 114-117.  If you\&#039;re not going to participate and help us Johnny-come-latelies, I\&#039;m not going to waste my time.  There\&#039;s a bunch of us hung up on 111, 125-126, 129-132, 203-204, 205, 214-215, 218, and 219.  So help out and I\&#039;ll help you out.  Fair enough?
